query: SELECT city, COUNT(*) as properties, SUM(COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM property_images WHERE property_images.property_id = properties.id), 0)) as total_images FROM properties WHERE source = 'zillow' GROUP BY city ORDER BY properties DESC;
